## Do's and Don'ts

### ✅ DO

```tsx
// ✅ Use existing liquid glass classes
<Card className="liquid-glass-card liquid-glass-card-elevated">

// ✅ Combine with design system
<div className="liquid-glass-content p-6">
  <IconContainer icon={Plus} variant="success" />
</div>

// ✅ Use semantic colors with glass
<h3 className="text-neutral-800">Title</h3>
```

### ❌ DON'T

```tsx
// ❌ Create new glass effect classes
<div className="my-custom-glass-effect">

// ❌ Hardcode backdrop-filter
<div style={{ backdropFilter: 'blur(10px)' }}>

// ❌ Use without .liquid-glass-content wrapper
<Card className="liquid-glass-card">
  <div className="p-6"> // Missing liquid-glass-content
</Card>
```

